  "instructions": [
    "In a medium saucepan, melt the butter over medium heat.",
    "Add the garlic, chili flakes, salt, and pepper, and sauté for 1 minute, until fragrant.",
    "Add the mussels, cover the saucepan, and cook for 3-4 minutes, until the mussels are cooked through.",
    "Uncover the saucepan and add the lemon juice, stir to combine.",
    "Meanwhile, cook the seffa paste according to the package instructions.",
    "To assemble the seffa, place a piece of cooked bun on a serving plate, then spoon the seffa paste over the bun.",
    "Top the seffa paste with the mussels, scallions, and a sprinkle of paprika."
